headline: What Are Wall Street Analysts' Target Price for Ball Corporation Stock?
summary: Despite Ball Corporation’s underperformance relative to the broader market over the past year, Wall Street analysts maintain a moderately optimistic outlook about the stock’s prospects.

headline: Industrial Packaging Q2 Earnings: Ball (NYSE:BALL) is the Best in the Biz
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Ball (NYSE:BALL) and the best and worst performers in the industrial packaging industry.
